				<p>" La duración de la batería es impresionante. Puedo usarlo todo el día sin problemas. "</p>
				<div class="flex mt-2" title="Calificación 5 estrellas">
					<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10 15l-5.878 3.09 1.122-6.545L.488 6.91l6.561-.955L10 0l2.951 5.955 6.561.955-4.756 4.635 1.122 6.545z"/></svg>
					<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10 15l-5.878 3.09 1.122-6.545L.488 6.91l6.561-.955L10 0l2.951 5.955 6.561.955-4.756 4.635 1.122 6.545z"/></svg>
					<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M10 15l-5.878 3.09 1.122-6.545L.488 6.91l6.561-.955L10 0l2.951 5.955 6.561.955-4.756 4.635 1.122 6.545z"/></svg>
